==English==
===Etymology===
Cf. F. [[adhésif]].

===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] /ædˈhi.sɪv/

===Adjective===
'''adhesive'''
# [[sticky|Sticky]]; [[tenacious]], as [[glutinous]] [[substances]].
# [[apt|Apt]] or [[tending]] to [[adhere]]; [[clinging]].

===Noun===
'''adhesive''' (''plural'' '''[[adhesives]]''')
# A [[substance]], such as [[glue]], that [[provides]] or [[promotes]] [[adhesion]].

